\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi0\sa200\rtlch\af9\afs22\lang1033\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs24\lang7177\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\rtlch \ltrch\loch \'93}}{{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177\i0\b0 Thus, the HSR Act and regulations add some clarity in distinguishing partial ownership acquisitions that are merely passive investments from those that confer control over the acquired firm.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177\i0\b0{\ul\ulc0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\fs22\i\loch\fs22\i  But the law remains highly uncertain and provides very little gu
